import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client'
import App from './App'
import { BrowserRouter } from 'react-browser-router'
import "./css/styles.css"

const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById("root"));
root.render(
    <React.StrictMode>
        <BrowserRouter>
        
        <App />

        </BrowserRouter>
    </React.StrictMode>
)
